Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.01,0:00:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.50,0:00:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然痛咯 手術才剛過去兩天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.41,0:00:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩天？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.35,0:00:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.73,0:00:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么我動也不能動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.16,0:00:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 去問醫生吧
